Steps to install GnuCobolIDE (there will be an installable package later on).

1. Download GnuCobolIDE and pyqode3 from https://github.com/Webhuis
2. cp scripts/gnucobolide to /usr/local/bin
3. cp package pyqode3 to /usr/lib/python3/dist-packages
4. cp the contents of the gnucobolide directory to /usr/local/lib/python3.10/dist-packages/gnucobolide

In a terminal run gnucobolide

